text:
A South Florida newspaper is pleading with Gov. Ron DeSantis to do more amid the coronavirus surge.

The Sun Sentinel editorial board asked him to issue a statewide face mask mandate in an editorial titled, "Help us out, Gov. DeSantis. We're dying here." https://t.co/QoFVQ1IyYE
